      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "10291-10330",
      "markText": "令人震惊的是德国负责宣传的官员竟然动用一切手段散布消息指责比利时人在进行狙击。",
      "totalCount": 2064,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300178015&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=10291&rangeEnd=10330",
