    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300178015_14_1934-1970",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "1934-1970",
      "markText": "他们允许著名的“密封车厢”将列宁和他的40名同事从瑞士穿越德国送到俄国。",
      "totalCount": 2060,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300178015&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1934&rangeEnd=1970",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ac32ed0813abac09g01534d?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1934&rangeEnd=1970"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300178015_12_12445-12481",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "12445-12481",
      "markText": "过去的这次大战证明，当交战国是一个异质的国家时，煽动脱离国家是如何有效。",
      "totalCount": 2053,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300178015&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=12445&rangeEnd=12481",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ac32ed0813abac09g01534d?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=12445&rangeEnd=12481"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300178015_8_24952-25026",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "24952-25026",
      "markText": "1914年8月10日，下院议员L.G. 基奥扎·莫尼（L.G. Chiozza Money）在伦敦《每日纪事报》上发表的一项声明，就是这一类的东西。",
      "totalCount": 2050,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300178015&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=24952&rangeEnd=25026",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ac32ed0813abac09g01534d?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=24952&rangeEnd=25026"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300178015_8_26648-26682",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "26648-26682",
      "markText": "在每一个交战国的宗教类报刊中都能找到大量适用于这种目的的文章为例证。",
      "totalCount": 2050,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300178015&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=26648&rangeEnd=26682",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ac32ed0813abac09g01534d?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=26648&rangeEnd=26682"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300178015_19_26732-26764",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "26732-26764",
      "markText": "法国抓住任何可能的机会美化这些美国士兵，鼓励他们写下自己的经历。",
      "totalCount": 2050,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300178015&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=26732&rangeEnd=26764",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ac32ed0813abac09g01534d?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=26732&rangeEnd=26764"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300178015_8_25709-25890",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "25709-25890",
      "markText": "兼并主义者要求得到的东西是：比利时全境，从索姆河口（the mouth of the Somme）向东直到比利时边界一线的法国北部地区，沿马斯河（the Maas）直到它与在帕尼—图勒（Pagny-Toul）地区的摩泽尔河（the Mosel）的交汇处，然后，通过吕内维尔（Lunéville）东部沿孚日山脉（the Vosges）直到贝尔福（Belfort）。",
      "totalCount": 2047,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300178015&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=25709&rangeEnd=25890",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ac32ed0813abac09g01534d?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=25709&rangeEnd=25890"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300178015_19_34702-34767",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "34702-34767",
      "markText": "一部名为《祖国》（Patria）的德国电影中的有趣的故事就体现了这一目的。",
      "totalCount": 2040,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300178015&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=34702&rangeEnd=34767",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ac32ed0813abac09g01534d?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=34702&rangeEnd=34767"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300178015_4_14098-14183",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "14098-14183",
      "markText": "如前所述，拉斯韦尔在1926年对宣传下的定义是：“它仅仅指通过重要的符号，或者更具体但不那么准确地说，就是通过故事、谣言、报道、图片以及社会传播的其他形式，来控制意见。”",
      "totalCount": 2029,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300178015&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14098&rangeEnd=14183",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ac32ed0813abac09g01534d?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14098&rangeEnd=14183"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300178015_10_9135-9167",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "9135-9167",
      "markText": "当那一天晚些时候敌人的损失开始传来的时候，公众的惊恐才有所缓和。",
      "totalCount": 2029,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300178015&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=9135&rangeEnd=9167",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ac32ed0813abac09g01534d?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=9135&rangeEnd=9167"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300178015_4_3794-3856",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3794-3856",
      "markText": "而且梅里亚姆在第一次世界大战期间，曾在意大利为美国宣传机构公共信息委员会工作，他十分关注解释政治行为时士气、宣传等的重要性。",
      "totalCount": 2022,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300178015&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3794&rangeEnd=3856",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ac32ed0813abac09g01534d?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3794&rangeEnd=3856"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300178015_19_21946-22220",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "21946-22220",
      "markText": "玛丽·罗伯茨·莱因哈特（Mary Roberts Rinehart）［《国王、王后和爪牙》（Kings, Queens and Pawns），1915］和几十个宣传者对协约国事业大书特书，也有少量的人帮助德国阐述其立场。",
      "totalCount": 2022,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300178015&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=21946&rangeEnd=22220",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ac32ed0813abac09g01534d?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=21946&rangeEnd=22220"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300178015_4_14784-15055",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "14784-15055",
      "markText": "梅尔文·L. 德弗勒和埃弗雷特·E. 丹尼斯的定义是：“以改变受众的信仰、态度和行为为目的的大众传播内容（不论是新闻报道、广告、戏剧还是别的形式）。”",
      "totalCount": 2012,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300178015&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14784&rangeEnd=15055",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ac32ed0813abac09g01534d?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14784&rangeEnd=15055"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300178015_12_20257-20394",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "20257-20394",
      "markText": "你将气球带到指定的地点，比如战线以后10英里，你知道你的气球会升到比如说6000英尺的高空，在那个高度将携带的传单发射出去。",
      "totalCount": 2009,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300178015&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=20257&rangeEnd=20394",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4ac32ed0813abac09g01534d?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=20257&rangeEnd=20394"
    },
    {
